    "The results show that \"HCRs have greater mobility, in the majority of cases they belong to the group who has been in the field for 11 to 15 years, they are highly productive, publishing on average over 100 articles each and interdisciplinary research plays a definite role in their careers\" (Must, 2020, p. 198).",
